OL,6,FTrevor Marsden contracted Hepatitis C
OL,7,Fafter taking part in a clinical trial
OL,8,Fin the 1970s.
OL,10,FHe said: "You do not tell everybody
OL,11,Feverything about yourself if you are
OL,12,Fill. Especially if you are a
OL,13,Fhemophiliac.
OL,15,F"People will not want to hear that you
OL,16,Fare contaminated with this or
OL,17,Fwhatever. You know it is not the sort
OL,18,Fof thing that you want to bring up."
