OL,3,C'Long over due, but they can't give us
OL,4,Cback the time we lost'
OL,6,FLouise, Trevor's wife, explained the
OL,7,Fimpact Kevin's illness had on family
OL,8,Flife.
OL,10,F"I had four children. Two who were
OL,11,Ftrying to help me look after their dad
OL,12,Fand the other two who were toddlers
OL,13,Fsitting on their beds crying- "Is my
OL,14,FDaddy going to die?""
OL,16,FShe described the compensation scheme
OL,17,Fas "long overdue" but added "the one
OL,18,Fthing they cannot do is give us back
OL,19,Four quality time".
