OL,4,Cback the time we lost'
OL,6,FInfected people ` both living and dead
OL,7,F` will start receiving payments
OL,8,Fthrough the new framework by the end
OL,9,Fof this year, while for others
OL,10,Faffected by the scandal, payments will
OL,11,Fbegin in 2025, the Cabinet Office said
OL,12,Fon Friday.
OL,14,FWhat will victims be able to claim for?
OL,16,FVictims with a serious Hepatitis B or
OL,17,FC infection could claim as much as
OL,18,F#1.6 million and someone with an HIV
OL,19,Finfection could get up to #2.6 million.
